<h1 class="govuk-heading-xl">DfE scholarship funding is not available</h1>

<p class="govuk-body">To be eligible for scholarship funding for the <b><%= course_name %></b> you must work in one of these settings in England:</p>

<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
  <li>state-funded schools</li>
  <li>state-funded 16 to 19 organisations</li>
  <li>independent special schools</li>
  <li>virtual schools</li>
  <li>hospital schools</li>
  <li>young offenders institutions</li>
</ul>

<div class="govuk-inset-text">
  From the answers you have given us you should be eligible for scholarship funding for the NPQ Early Years Leadership (NPQEYL). You can <%= link_to('go back and select the NPQEYLQ', registration_wizard_show_path(@wizard.previous_step_path)) %> or continue with your registration for NPQ for <%= course_name %>.
</div>

